    <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="groovy" name="Verify Input" id="verifyInput">
      <script>//****** groovy: Verify Input, script to get invite_COL collection for looping
package processes.scripts;
import groovy.json.*;
def jsonSlurper = new JsonSlurper();
def inviteResponseArray_s = [];
def inviteArrayList_s = new java.util.ArrayList();
def inviteList_s = execution.getVariable("inviteList").replaceAll(" ","");
if (inviteList_s.length() > 5 ) {
	def invite_s = "";
	def searchFrom = 0;
	def nextposition = 0;
	while ( nextposition >= 0 ) {
		AnswerGroovyJson = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(jsonSlurper.parseText("{\"InviteEmail\":\"\",\"inviteResponse\":{}}"));
		nextposition = inviteList_s.indexOf(",", searchFrom)
		if (nextposition > 0) {
			invite_s = inviteList_s.substring(searchFrom,nextposition);
		} else {
			invite_s = inviteList_s.substring(searchFrom);
		}
		searchFrom = nextposition + 1;
		inviteArrayList_s.add(invite_s);
		AnswerGroovyJson.content.InviteEmail = invite_s;
		AnswerGroovyJson.content.inviteResponse.ur_status = "Invited";
		inviteResponseArray_s.add(AnswerGroovyJson.content);
	}
} else {
		inviteArrayList_s.add(execution.getVariable("wf_currentAssignee"));
}
execution.setVariable("invites_COL", inviteArrayList_s);
def inviteResponseArray_j = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(inviteResponseArray_s);
execution.setVariable("inviteResponseArray", play.api.libs.json.Json.parse(inviteResponseArray_j.toPrettyString()) );
</script>

      <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="groovy" name="Set Response" id="setResponse">
        <script>//**************** when answer, send all ur_ vars into responseArray by ID
package processes.scripts;
import groovy.json.*;
def jsonSlurper = new JsonSlurper();

def inviteResponseArrayGroovyJson = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(jsonSlurper.parseText(play.api.libs.json.Json.stringify(execution.getVariable('inviteResponseArray'))))
def inviteResponseArray_s = []
def currentInvite_s = execution.getVariable('currentInvite')
def AnswerGroovyJson = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(jsonSlurper.parseText("{\"InviteEmail\":\"\",\"inviteResponse\":{}}"));
AnswerGroovyJson.content.InviteEmail = currentInvite_s;

def inviteResponseVars_s = new java.util.HashMap();
execution.getVariables().each{ k, v -> 
    if(k.indexOf("ur_") >= 0){
	    inviteResponseVars_s.put(k,v);
    }
};

AnswerGroovyJson.content.InviteEmail = currentInvite_s;
AnswerGroovyJson.content.inviteResponse = inviteResponseVars_s;
AnswerGroovyJson.content.inviteResponse.ur_status = "Responded";

inviteResponseArrayGroovyJson.content.each {invite ->
	if(invite.InviteEmail != currentInvite) {
		inviteResponseArray_s.add(invite)
	}
}
inviteResponseArray_s.add(AnswerGroovyJson.content)
def inviteResponseArray_j = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(inviteResponseArray_s);
execution.setVariable("inviteResponseArray", play.api.libs.json.Json.parse(inviteResponseArray_j.toPrettyString()) );
</script>

    <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="javascript" name="initial Settings js" id="initialSettings">
      <script>// *** set titles and initial status
if (null == execution.getVariable("interactionTitle")) 	execution.setVariable("interactionTitle",  "Give some feedback");
if (null == execution.getVariable("interactionStatus")) execution.setVariable("interactionStatus", "Initialized_Process");

// *** email and notification settings
if (null == execution.getVariable("notifyWhenAllResponded")) 		execution.setVariable("notifyWhenAllResponded", "YES");
if (null == execution.getVariable("notifyInviteFirst")) 			execution.setVariable("notifyInviteFirst", "YES");
if (null == execution.getVariable("notifyOriginatorWhenResponded")) execution.setVariable("notifyOriginatorWhenResponded", "YES");
if (null == execution.getVariable("emailFrom")) execution.setVariable("emailFrom", "alert@point.io");

//*** timer settings
// first step 1 hour timeout to prevent process not needed stay for ever
	if (null == execution.getVariable("firstStepTimeout")) execution.setVariable("firstStepTimeout", "PT1H");
// send a reminder after 3 days
	if (null == execution.getVariable("reminderTimeDuration")) execution.setVariable("reminderTimeDuration", "P3D");   
// reminder, default to repeat 3 times, every 2 days, start from 1/11, should be able to get js date for today.
	if (null == execution.getVariable("reminderTimeCycle")) execution.setVariable("reminderTimeCycle", "R3/2016-01-11T02:00:00Z/P2D");
// cancel entire process after 15 days
	if (null == execution.getVariable("cancelTimeDuration")) execution.setVariable("cancelTimeDuration", "P15D");    

//*** UI default settings, env sensitive, moving between env will need this to be updated, if not start from app/template with UI settings

	if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_interactionAddContent_formid")) execution.setVariable("poi_interactionAddContent_formid", "formid123");    
	if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_interactionAddInvite_formid"))  execution.setVariable("poi_interactionAddInvite_formid", "formid123");    
	if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_interactionConfirm_formid"))    execution.setVariable("poi_interactionConfirm_formid", "formid123");    
	if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_interactionReview_formid"))     execution.setVariable("poi_interactionReview_formid", "formid123");    
	if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_interaction_formid"))           execution.setVariable("poi_interaction_formid", "formid123");    

// *** temp testing settings
if (null == execution.getVariable("inputConfirmationDecision")) execution.setVariable("inputConfirmationDecision", "confirmed");
if (null == execution.getVariable("inputReviewDecision")) 		execution.setVariable("inputReviewDecision", "closed");

if (null == execution.getVariable("inviteList")) 		execution.setVariable("inviteList", "demo1@point.io, demo2@point.io, demo3@point.io");

execution.removeVariable("poi_template_icon");
</script>
